data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! SELLERS ARE MOTIVATED! Transform your purchase into an inviting In-Law Suite or an opportunity for extra income! Prepare to be impressed by this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 2-car garage home, boasting luxurious features throughout. ROOF: 5 YEARS - HVAC: INSTALLED 08/17/2023, ELECTRICAL PANEL: UPGRADED 2 YEARS AGO - WATER TANK: ORIGINAL - EXT PAINT: 5 YEARS L- INT PAINT: 4 YEARS - IRRIGATION: YES (ON WELL).  NEW FRONT DOORS AND SLIDER DOORS.  This home sits on almost a quarter acre that is fenced in the backyard. The furniture may even be included. The extended 3-car wide driveway, along with a circular drive, can accommodate all your family's vehicles. Additionally, the side fence offers RV or outdoor toy storage. Experience a hassle-free living environment with NO HOA, NO flood insurance, NO sinkhole, NO CDD fees, and LOW taxes! The community offers multiple access points for convenience. The house has great curb appeal with lots of palm trees. Upon entering through the double wooden front doors, you will surely be captivated by the stunning porcelain 24 x 44 high gloss tiles that adorn the entire home, except for the bedrooms and front room. The living room/dining room combo showcases beautiful wood-look floors, complete with a fan/light kit in the front and a chandelier in the back. To the right, is the Ensuite, In-Law suite, or potential rental space. This area features a spacious bedroom, walk-in closet, sitting area, an updated shower bathroom, and an enclosed porch that has been transformed into a fully updated kitchen and sitting area. The kitchen comes complete with double sinks, a garbage disposal, a microwave, a glass top stove, can lights, two windows, a table area, ceramic tile, a washer/dryer, a hanging TV, and a sitting room. Two exterior doors ensure privacy, private entrance and minimal disruption to the remainder of the home. The main home boasts a bright dream gourmet kitchen, featuring a long narrow wood table that conveniently fits in the insert with three stools, perfect for additional seating or a coffee/wine bar. The kitchen is equipped with 1 year old stainless steel appliances that complement the granite countertops, commercial faucets, large cabinets, and an enormous island with 7 deep drawers, including a shelf for the microwave. Modern hardware and can lights add a touch of luxury to this favorite room of the house, which overlooks the family room featuring a stand alone fireplace and slider doors providing a view of the spacious backyard surrounded by neighboring fences. The second bedroom is located off the family room, while bedrooms 3 and 4 are positioned down a hallway with a bathroom and hall closet. This prime location places you near shopping, restaurants, the Gulf of Mexico, malls, and numerous attractions. Tampa is just a 30-minute drive away. Your dream home awaits, offering endless possibilities!
